{
  "name": "Heartbeat on every run",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Heartbeat on every run (dead-man's switch)\n\nDrop a NoCrash **Heartbeat** node at the **end** of any critical workflow. Every time the workflow finishes, it pings NoCrash to say \"I ran.\"\n\nIf the ping ever stops arriving — because the workflow silently stopped, the trigger broke, or the instance went down — NoCrash notices the missing heartbeat and alerts you. **You find out it stopped, even when there's no error to catch.**\n\n**What you need**\n- A *NoCrash API* credential (your `nc_` key) on the Heartbeat node.\n- The Monitor ID of the watch you created in NoCrash for this workflow.\n\nReplace the demo middle steps with your real work — the only thing that matters is that **Heartbeat is the last node**.\n\nRequires a free NoCrash account → https://nocrash.io/?utm_source=n8n-template&utm_medium=community&utm_campaign=node-launch-2026",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 440,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "note-overview",
      "name": "How this works",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-280, -60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Your real work goes here\nThis HTTP step stands in for whatever your\ncritical workflow actually does. Swap it\nfor your real steps — keep Heartbeat last.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 280,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "note-work",
      "name": "Replace this step",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [440, -80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "hoursInterval": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "trigger-hourly",
      "name": "Run this workflow hourly",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [240, 160]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://api.example.com/do-the-work",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 30000
        }
      },
      "id": "do-the-work",
      "name": "Do the critical work",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [480, 160],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 3000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "heartbeat",
        "monitorId": "REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_MONITOR_ID",
        "executionId": "={{ $execution.id }}",
        "durationMs": 0,
        "metadata": "{}"
      },
      "id": "send-heartbeat",
      "name": "Send heartbeat to NoCrash",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-nocrash.nocrash",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [720, 160],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 3000,
      "credentials": {
        "nocrashApi": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_NOCRASH_API_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "NoCrash API"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Run this workflow hourly": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Do the critical work",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Do the critical work": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Send heartbeat to NoCrash",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1",
    "timezone": "UTC",
    "executionTimeout": 300,
    "saveExecutionProgress": true,
    "saveDataSuccessExecution": "all",
    "saveDataErrorExecution": "all"
  },
  "pinData": {},
  "meta": {
    "templateCredsSetupCompleted": false
  }
}
